<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>File-Status on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/file-status/</link><description>Recent content in File-Status on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/file-status/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] COBOL FILE-STATUS 35 — File Not Found Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/file-not-found/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/file-not-found/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="file-status-35--file-not-found-error"&gt;FILE-STATUS 35 — File Not Found Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;FILE-STATUS 35&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when the COBOL runtime attempts to open a file that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist at the specified path, or the path is incorrect. This is one of the most common file-related errors in COBOL programs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In COBOL, file operations are managed through the File Status field. When an &lt;code&gt;OPEN&lt;/code&gt; statement is executed and the runtime cannot find the file (for INPUT or I-O mode) or create it (for OUTPUT mode), FILE-STATUS is set to &lt;code&gt;35&lt;/code&gt;. This is typically a configuration or path issue rather than a code logic problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] COBOL FILE-STATUS 39 — Record Length Mismatch Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/file-status-39/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/file-status-39/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="file-status-39--record-length-mismatch-error"&gt;FILE-STATUS 39 — Record Length Mismatch Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;FILE-STATUS 39&lt;/code&gt; error occurs when the record length defined in the COBOL program doesn&amp;rsquo;t match the actual record length in the file. The runtime rejects the open or read operation because the sizes are incompatible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In COBOL, each file has a record layout defined in the FD (File Description) section. The file on disk also has a record length (either fixed or determined by line delimiters). If these two lengths don&amp;rsquo;t match, the runtime sets FILE-STATUS to &lt;code&gt;39&lt;/code&gt; when attempting to open or read the file.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Duplicate key error in COBOL</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/cobol-duplicate-key/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/cobol-duplicate-key/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When writing to an indexed (ISAM/VSAM) file, a duplicate key error (file status &amp;lsquo;22&amp;rsquo;) occurs if the new record&amp;rsquo;s key matches an existing record&amp;rsquo;s key.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writing record with existing key value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Duplicate primary key in indexed file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Not reading/rewriting to update existing record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing duplicate key handling in WRITE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; WRONG: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;No&lt;/span&gt; duplicate &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; check&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WRITE&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-REC&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INVALID&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Duplicate key&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; CORRECT: Check &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;file&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;after&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;write
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WRITE&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-REC&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INVALID&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; FILE-STATUS &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;22&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Duplicate key - record exists&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;REWRITE&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-REC&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ELSE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Write error: &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; FILE-STATUS&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-IF
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-WRITE&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; CORRECT: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Read&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;before&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;write&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;update
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IS&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-ID&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INVALID&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WRITE&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-REC&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INVALID&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;REWRITE&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-REC&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-READ&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; Writing duplicate &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;record
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MOVE &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;CUST001&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TO&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-ID.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WRITE&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-REC.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;If&lt;/span&gt; CUST001 already exists: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;file&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;22
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/file-not-found"&gt;File Not Found&lt;/a&gt; - file errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/invalid-key"&gt;Invalid Key&lt;/a&gt; - key access errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>File not found in COBOL</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/cobol-file-not-found/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cobol/cobol-file-not-found/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;COBOL file not found errors occur when the OPEN INPUT or OPEN I-O statement cannot find the file. The FILE-STATUS field will contain &amp;lsquo;35&amp;rsquo; (file not found).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;File path incorrect in DD statement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;File doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist on disk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;JCL DD assignment missing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;File was deleted or moved&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Case sensitivity in file name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; Check &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;file&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;after&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;open
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INPUT&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; FILE-STATUS &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;NOT &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;00&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;File open error: &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; FILE-STATUS&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;STOP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RUN
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-IF&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; CORRECT: Verify &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;file&lt;/span&gt; exists &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;before&lt;/span&gt; opening&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OPEN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INPUT&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-FILE&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; FILE-STATUS &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;35&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISPLAY &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;File not found&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;STOP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RUN
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;END-IF&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; Process &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;file
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CLOSE&lt;/span&gt; CUSTOMER-FILE.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cobol" data-lang="cobol"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IDENTIFICATION&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DIVISION&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
